Section 3    GOOD NUTRITION STARTS WITH THE BASICS
                                            By Jan Rosenstreich

                                        http://www.castle.net/~mystic/
Jan's exposure to the world of metaphysics started in the late 1970's
with meditation through the Transcendental Meditation Movement.
Since then he has pursued his studies of Reflexology at the Well Person
Place, Reiki II, and completed a 3 year course of study that covered a
